                     <interp inst="t18270913-360-off1999" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270913-360-off1999" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18270913-360-cd2000" type="crimeDate">25th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-360-off1999 t18270913-360-cd2000"></join>, 5 shirts, value 2l. 5s.; 2 handkerchiefs, value 7s.; 3 towels, value 2s., and 3 pairs of stockings, value 3s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18270913-360-victim2597" type="victimName">
